In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.

Almighty Father, Giver of every good thing, show us Thy mercy and grant, we beseech Thee, through the merits of Thy faithful servant, Saint Frances Xavier Cabrini, that all who invoke her intercession may obtain what they desire according to the good pleasure of Thy Holy Will (mention request here‚Ä¶)

